{"article_id":"oGPc5HycRGH5zQfS","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Colorado Springs , Colorado","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"( CNN )","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"Ted Cruz on Saturday clinched the support of every pledged delegate in Colorado ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"capturing all of the final 13 delegates","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"who will go to the national convention in July","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"and demonstrating his organizational strength in the all-important delegate race .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"Even though voters did n't head to the polls Saturday ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Cruz 's strength here could help deny Donald Trump the 1,237 delegates","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"that he needs","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"to clinch the nomination .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"Cruz 's victory Saturday ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"combined with delegates","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"he had already earned ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"hands him 30 of the 37 delegates across the state","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"who are legally bound to support him on the first ballot at the convention ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"along with four other delegates","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"who gave him verbal commitments of support .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"`` Today was another resounding victory for conservatives , Republicans , and Americans","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"who care about the future of our country , ''","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"the Cruz campaign said a statement .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"`` Utah , North Dakota , Wisconsin , and tonight 's incredible results in Colorado have proven this :","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Republicans are uniting behind our campaign","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"because they want a leader with real solutions","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"who will bring back jobs , freedom , and security . ''","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Earlier in the afternoon , Cruz had urged state Republicans here at the Broadmoor Arena to help him defeat Trump .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"`` If we continue to stand united ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"we are going to win this Republican nomination .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"We are going to win the general election .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"We are going to win the state of Colorado","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"and we are going to turn this country around , ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Cruz said to huge cheers from the arena floor .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Cruz , Trump make mad dash for delegates","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Cruz , Trump make mad dash for delegates","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"03:57","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"In yet another sign of his airtight ground game , Cruz spoke before a huge screen","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"displaying his slate of delegates for the final 13 spots ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"and he noted","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"that his slate was also printed on the bright orange T-shirts","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"that his many volunteers were wearing on the state convention floor .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"Trump 's campaign , by contrast , initially distributed fliers","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"listing the campaign 's national delegate candidates","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"that were riddled with errors .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"The flier","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"displaying the Trump slate","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"is supposed to be the tip sheet","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"that party members use","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"to fill out their ballot .","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"But on the first slate","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"that the Trump campaign was giving out ,","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"more than a half dozen of their delegate candidates were listed with the wrong delegate number .","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"At least one of the delegate numbers corresponded to a delegate","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"supporting Cruz .","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"The Trump campaign reprinted the flier ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"but the second flier also included several errors .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Before the voting began ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Trump campaign adviser Patrick Davis said in an interview","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that the team had been given `` incomplete '' information by the Colorado Republican Party about delegate numbers .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Later in the evening ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"as the votes were being counted ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"senior Trump adviser Alan Cobb said","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"several supporters had told the campaign","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that their ballot number had changed numerous times","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"or that their name did not appear on the party 's official list of national delegate candidates","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"even though they had filled out the proper paperwork .","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"Alan Cobb , the senior adviser to Trump , said","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"the campaign was looking into the reports of balloting problems","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"and was not ruling out a challenge","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"to seating the Colorado delegation at the national convention in July .","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"A spokesman for the state party said","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"it was looking into the reports","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"but had no immediate comment .","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"It was unclear how much confusion that caused ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"but the Trump campaign has acknowledged","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that it did not expect to win any delegates in Colorado .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"While there was fervent enthusiasm for Cruz ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"former New Hampshire Sen. John E. Sununu ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"who was Ohio Gov . John Kasich 's surrogate at the gathering ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"was greeted with polite applause .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"`` We 've got to unify behind that candidate","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"who will win , ''","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Sununu told the crowd ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"pointing to Kasich 's strength in general election polling matchups with Hillary Clinton .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Kasich , however , had not won any delegates as of Saturday afternoon .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"Trump campaign surrogate Stephen Miller , a policy adviser to the real estate magnate , drew a warmer response","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"by opening his speech with a focus on the issue","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that helped carry Trump to the top of the Republican field :","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Immigration .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"`` Do you think","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"the United States of America needs to secure its border ? ''","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Miller asked the crowd ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"which shouted `` Yes '' in response .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Before even mentioning Trump 's candidacy ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Miller went on to read letters from parents","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"who","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"he said","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"had lost their children to `` illegal immigrant violence . ''","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"`` These Americans deserve a voice","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"and I am going to give it to them today , ''","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Miller said .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"`` It 's the powerless","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"who are standing up behind Mr . Trump . ''","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"Cruz dominated the intricate delegate selection process of the Colorado Republican Party ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"and in this pivotal swing state , a strong campaign organization has often made the difference between defeat and victory in the race to the White House .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"In this first round for the GOP , Team Cruz once again proved its mettle","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"-- far outpacing the efforts of Trump and Kasich in the scramble for delegates at each of the congressional district gatherings this week .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"By late Friday , Cruz had swept all the available delegates in the state 's seven congressional districts .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"In the final rounds of a messy and chaotic process Friday , candidates","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"vying to be one of Colorado 's delegates","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"lined up along the walls of the ballroom at a Doubletree hotel here","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"waiting their turn","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"to deliver campaign speeches .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"`` You have 10 seconds .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Go ! ''","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"a party official barked","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"as the first candidate stepped to the microphone Friday morning .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Cruz volunteers seemed to be everywhere ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"working the hallways","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"where party members were crammed shoulder to shoulder among vendors","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"peddling Cruz infinity scarves and Trump-style `` Make America Great Again '' hats .","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"In one corner , a hot pink handwritten sign lured the undecided over","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"to talk to `` Cruz Persuasion Teams . ''","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"The ballroom floor was littered Cruz campaign slates","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"( the tip sheets","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"indicating","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"which delegates are endorsed by the campaign ) .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"Scattered across the room were glossy copies of the `` Donald Trump Voter Guide , ''","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"which is actually an anti-Trump pamphlet","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"distributed by one of the super PACs","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"that is trying to defeat him .","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"Amid all the jostling , shouting and chaos throughout the day Friday , delegates","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"aligned with Cruz","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"won again and again .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Trump still maintains a wide lead over Cruz in the delegate count","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"as the two candidates attempt to win the 1,237 delegates","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"needed","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"to clinch the Republican nomination .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"But at a time","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"when a contested convention looks increasingly likely ,","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"there was palpable disdain for Trump 's candidacy among the GOP faithful here .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"His string of unforced errors , nasty tweets and controversial policy statements in recent weeks have clearly taken a toll .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"`` The momentum against Trump at the activist level is just frothing , ''","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"said Josh Penry , a former state senator","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"who was Marco Rubio 's state chairman in Colorado .","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"`` There was a time","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"when Trump could have competed in Colorado .","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"That time has long since passed .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"... Among the activists , the tide has turned against him dramatically . ''","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Trump canceled a planned rally in Colorado this week","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"as he focused his efforts on New York ,","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"which holds its critical primary on April 19 .","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"While Trump had some fervent supporters here at the state convention ,","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"it was clear from the speeches","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"delivered by delegate candidates","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"that his appeal has worn thin for many Republicans","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"-- a testament to how much work the real estate magnate would have to do","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"to unite the party","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"if he becomes the nominee .","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"At Thursday night 's gathering for Colorado 's 7th Congressional District , 19-year-old student Angel Merlos urged the crowd to elect him as a Cruz delegate to the convention ,","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"because","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"he said","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"the nation 's values and morals were at stake","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"if Trump were to become the Republican nominee .","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"`` Morality is about how you act , how you speak , and how you carry yourself , ''","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"Merlos said in interview after his brief speech in Arvada .","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"`` I believe","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"Trump has no morals","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"because he lies about many things . ... He contradicts himself on everything . ''","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"`` He thinks","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"he knows what will help the immigration problem ,","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"but he does n't , ''","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"Merlos continued .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"`` He talks about a wall","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"-- that may do something .","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"I do n't know exactly what it will do .","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"But he uses immigrants","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"to help him build his buildings ,","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"and yet he 's so cruel and harsh ''","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"when he talks about them ,","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"Merlos said .","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"Delegate candidate David Head ran as an `` unpledged '' delegate in the hope","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"of serving as a voice against Trump on the floor of Republican convention in July .","depth":6},{"id":184,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"he would be a disaster for both the Republican Party and the country , ''","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"said Head ,","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"who owns an insurance business in Westminster , Colorado , with his son .","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":189,"text":"This is how to win delegates at a convention","depth":8},{"id":190,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"This is how to win delegates at a convention","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"06:10","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"`` He confuses intimidation and bluster with straight talk and honesty .","depth":7},{"id":195,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"he is anti-woman .","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"he is saying whatever he thinks","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"will sell","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"to get him a vote ,","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"and I think","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"he 's playing on the fears and prejudices of a lot of people","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"to intimidate people into voting for him . ''","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"Libby Szabo , a Jefferson County Commissioner","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"who won a slot as a Cruz delegate to the national convention ,","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":207,"text":"as a conservative , she was troubled by Trump 's recent comments","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"about punishing women","depth":10},{"id":209,"text":"who have illegal abortions .","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"( Trump backed off that position after an uproar from opposite sides of the political spectrum . )","depth":8},{"id":211,"text":"`` I like","depth":8},{"id":212,"text":"that he has started a dialogue in our party","depth":9},{"id":213,"text":"that we need to have .","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"I just do n't see him as being consistent , ''","depth":9},{"id":215,"text":"Szabo said .","depth":9},{"id":216,"text":"`` One week he says one thing ,","depth":9},{"id":217,"text":"the next week he says another thing . ''","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"Beyond the simmering anti-Trump sentiment here , Cruz 's strength in the delegate chase in Colorado","depth":7},{"id":219,"text":"( as well as states like North Dakota , Louisiana and Tennessee )","depth":7},{"id":220,"text":"has once again exposed the deficiencies of Trump 's organizing operation ,","depth":7},{"id":221,"text":"which is scrambling to catch up .","depth":7},{"id":222,"text":"Trump 's allies insist","depth":8},{"id":223,"text":"there is still time","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"to streamline their delegate wrangling operation","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"and time","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"to persuade even those","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"who are resistant to his brand of politics at this moment .","depth":11},{"id":228,"text":"One Trump adviser said","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"they entered the Colorado GOP contests with the expectation","depth":11},{"id":230,"text":"of winning `` zero delegates ''","depth":11},{"id":231,"text":"-- and were pleased at the end of the day Friday","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"that they had won two alternate delegates","depth":12},{"id":233,"text":"pledged to Trump in Congressional District 4 .","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"`` This is just the beginning of a four-month process","depth":10},{"id":235,"text":"to convince the unpledged delegates and alternates in Colorado","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"that Donald Trump means what he says ,","depth":12},{"id":237,"text":"he 's going to make America great again , ''","depth":12},{"id":238,"text":"said Davis , a Colorado-based political consultant","depth":10},{"id":239,"text":"who joined the Trump team this week","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"after Trump 's campaign manager fired their Colorado state director .","depth":11},{"id":241,"text":"In conversations with Cruz supporters , Davis brushed off questions about Trump 's poor standing in general election match-ups with Hillary Clinton ,","depth":8},{"id":242,"text":"arguing","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"that `` polls","depth":12},{"id":244,"text":"taken today , six months away from November ,","depth":12},{"id":245,"text":"are garbage ,","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"and will not be predictive on election day . ''","depth":10},{"id":247,"text":"As for Cruz 's clear organizational advantage , Davis said","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"Trump 's team remains undaunted .","depth":9},{"id":249,"text":"`` This is an insider 's game , ''","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"Davis said ,","depth":12},{"id":251,"text":"as he waited for the final votes of the day to be tabulated .","depth":11},{"id":252,"text":"`` Nowhere in America ,","depth":12},{"id":253,"text":"including Colorado ,","depth":12},{"id":254,"text":"are insiders the heart and soul of the Trump campaign . ''","depth":11},{"id":255,"text":"But the question is whether Trump can get geared up in time","depth":10},{"id":256,"text":"to win that insider 's game .","depth":10},{"id":257,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":258,"text":"Trump campaign recalibrates","depth":6},{"id":259,"text":"to focus on delegates","depth":6},{"id":260,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":261,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":262,"text":"Trump campaign recalibrates","depth":8},{"id":263,"text":"to focus on delegates","depth":8},{"id":264,"text":"03:21","depth":6},{"id":265,"text":"His campaign announced an expanded role this week for veteran GOP operative Paul Manafort ,","depth":5},{"id":266,"text":"who is managing convention activities for Trump","depth":6},{"id":267,"text":"-- just as he did for the presidential campaigns of Gerald Ford , Ronald Reagan , George H.W . Bush and Bob Dole .","depth":6},{"id":268,"text":"Becky Mizel , a Trump volunteer","depth":8},{"id":269,"text":"who was the former chair of the Pueblo County Republican Party in Colorado ,","depth":8},{"id":270,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":271,"text":"she was n't discouraged by Trump 's poor showing in the state .","depth":6},{"id":272,"text":"`` Cruz has a very strong organization here , ''","depth":7},{"id":273,"text":"she said","depth":8},{"id":274,"text":"when asked about the obstacles","depth":9},{"id":275,"text":"her candidate had faced .","depth":9},{"id":276,"text":"One of Cruz 's most powerful allies ,","depth":9},{"id":277,"text":"she noted ,","depth":9},{"id":278,"text":"was the Rocky Mountain Gun Owners ,","depth":9},{"id":279,"text":"which circulated ubiquitous blue fliers","depth":10},{"id":280,"text":"touting Cruz delegates at every voting location this week .","depth":10},{"id":281,"text":"Mizel credited the head of the group , Dudley Brown","depth":11},{"id":282,"text":"( who she counts as a friend ) ,","depth":11},{"id":283,"text":"with `` organizing the Cruz machine with the legislators","depth":11},{"id":284,"text":"who have decided to go","depth":12},{"id":285,"text":"and block Mr . Trump . ''","depth":12},{"id":286,"text":"`` The average person on the street is working or raising their kids","depth":12},{"id":287,"text":"--","depth":12},{"id":288,"text":"they are n't political junkies","depth":12},{"id":289,"text":"like the caucus attendees are --","depth":12},{"id":290,"text":"and those are the people","depth":11},{"id":291,"text":"that are attracted to Mr. Trump , ''","depth":11},{"id":292,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":293,"text":"At the same time , Mizel said","depth":3},{"id":294,"text":"she was relieved that the Trump campaign now seems to grasp the gravity of the task before them","depth":4},{"id":295,"text":"as they prepare for the possibility of a contested convention .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":591,"left":552,"right":590,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":552,"left":399,"right":551,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":399,"left":326,"right":398,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":326,"left":319,"right":325,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":319,"left":312,"right":318,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":312,"left":297,"right":311,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":297,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":304,"right":310,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":300,"right":303,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":2,"right":299,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":298,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":298,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":6,"right":302,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":302,"left":7,"right":301,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":308,"right":309,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":306,"right":307,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":306,"left":10,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":314,"right":317,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":314,"left":313,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":313,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":317,"left":20,"right":316,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"pa